description: This file defines a SearchService class for in-memory book search functionality using stub data. It includes methods for searching books by title or author, case-insensitive, with some sample book data embedded as a list.

classes.name: SearchService
classes.description: A service class providing in-memory search capabilities over a list of Book objects, supporting search by title or author.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Returns a list of books where the title or author contains the query string, case-insensitive. If the query is empty, returns all books.
